name: Let's have some fun, let's have some love
description:
#11
A funny and loving intention made into an animated lettering funky style. 

1920x1920 Mp4 video in a loop of 7 seconds 

Piece #11 of the collection: I'm not your therapist but I'd like to cheer you up with my dorky art The series focuses on the fragility of the inner world and brings up topics that we often find in our long journey on earth.
